      <div class="md:col-span-1">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-display text-petal-rose mb-4">Petal Culture</h3>
        <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm font-body mb-4">
          Artful florals for life's beautiful moments. Creating bespoke arrangements for weddings and events.
        </p>
        <div class="flex space-x-4">
          <a href="#" aria-label="Instagram" class="text-stone-500 hover:text-petal-rose transition-colors">
